4,"uid":6221,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T18:02:52.000Z","msg":"反而我覺得一開始個Prologue, 廿分鐘左右<br />\n講同欣欣既感情發展到一齊再到發現係幻覺<br />\n之後出title，呢下真係好正，handle得啱啱好夠<br />\n太快太過too good to be true which is also the point<br />\n因為男主係個精神病患者，更加suspecible to呢個image (加上後面有解釋點解無懷疑過佢係幻覺)"},{"pid":"43eb84419a47de929cf29b3b623e4b906f7d7b63","tid":2101954,"uid":273807,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"56bcb8fe68d4d64726bde90817567d72a361184f","tid":2101954,"uid":204637,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T16:08:51.000Z","msg":"其實唔明葉嵐叫佢大學前男友還屋匙係咩 <br />\n如果係表示女主係臭雞 佢同教授扑嘢已經係啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T18:19:09.000Z","msg":"同教授扑嘢係臭雞 加埋前男友就係快換畫嘅臭雞"},{"pid":"ed3e9e12c0c7f74f0867c4c6da722d2adee910b5","tid":2101954,"uid":26523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T18:36:18.000Z","msg":"最尾係女有幻覺定係真係真實？"},{"pid":"036ce413aed97873ccba8f989aad1972a7d4ee33","tid":2101954,"uid":25375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T18:39:41.000Z","msg":"皮已正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68bde2ff8b9abd3a774cede3035c56f03a466140","tid":2101954,"uid":295650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T18:55:54.000Z","msg":"謙謙要gel 頭先令仔"},{"pid":"942289d38fb8a073a46913bcbb97e62d3dce6224","tid":2101954,"uid":114105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T18:59:36.000Z","msg":"其實葉嵐除咗同欣欣一樣樣之外，到底係咩令男主咁突然愛上佢？"},{"pid":"2a54ffb85ddeebbd0488533e91d440370b7700f3","tid":2101954,"uid":235565,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"942289d38fb8a073a46913bcbb97e62d3dce6224","tid":2101954,"uid":114105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T18:59:36.000Z","msg":"其實葉嵐除咗同欣欣一樣樣之外，到底係咩令男主咁突然愛上佢？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T23:18:59.000Z","msg":"男主角係鍾意葉嵐先，再幻想欣欣出黎，應該係一見鍾情，講feel姐"},{"pid":"00946b58d9e4e50bcaa208c1cf600b2b7a7920d5","tid":2101954,"uid":190333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"68bde2ff8b9abd3a774cede3035c56f03a466140","tid":2101954,"uid":295650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T18:55:54.000Z","msg":"謙謙要gel 頭先令仔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T01:51:27.000Z","msg":"Interview果幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0edbead4255a0354bd30944a502697c1f148b22b","tid":2101954,"uid":131247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"68bde2ff8b9abd3a774cede3035c56f03a466140","tid":2101954,"uid":295650,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T18:55:54.000Z","msg":"謙謙要gel 頭先令仔"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T02:35:36.000Z","msg":"有一幕gel 左頭幾似哥哥"},{"pid":"53ff65f8abb71d708b6f60f0dad3995bc9524105","tid":2101954,"uid":155928,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"56bcb8fe68d4d64726bde90817567d72a361184f","tid":2101954,"uid":204637,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T16:08:51.000Z","msg":"其實唔明葉嵐叫佢大學前男友還屋匙係咩 <br />\n如果係表示女主係臭雞 佢同教授扑嘢已經係啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:22:27.000Z","msg":"我覺得係借前男友把口嚟鋪墊啫。一嚟比觀眾知佢兩個月就換一個男朋友，二嚟就係前男友話佢，佢個樣係唔在意，其實佢好在意人哋點睇，自己都好嫌棄自己，覺得冇人會接受到真實嘅自己，個個都會咁睇佢，有一種還掂都係就繼續自甘墮落嘅感覺，再接住借暈等教授送佢。<br />\n<br />\n即使只係兩個月貨仔，名正言順嘅情侶關係同地下情婦嘅關係其實差好遠。會比鎖匙其實係信任，同淨係比佢上屋企幾個鐘又差好遠。<br />\n<br />\n後面再影佢覺得自己污穢唔配被愛，對比佢一開始個樣，都反映咗佢唔止係為利益，而係唔敢去愛，同時亦好需要被愛。所以當佢揾到一個接受到佢所有嘅人，佢先會奮不顧身到咁。<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得套戲好好睇，好欣賞細節位，唔太覺得係多餘，美中不足係葉嵐嘅內心感受可以講多少少。個人淺見，有少少長氣，唔好介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d54ab812807eecec1f2020b07d07cb98589740","tid":2101954,"uid":337444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:32:14.000Z","msg":"睇哂全部 撐下巴打先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都覺得有啲位係轉得太快 例如dr馮叫葉嵐小心反移情 下個鏡頭就一齊左 會唔會快左啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3418cf0e8eca7be1cbc7a85a8d871ac17325f932","tid":2101954,"uid":190333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6d54ab812807eecec1f2020b07d07cb98589740","tid":2101954,"uid":337444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:32:14.000Z","msg":"睇哂全部 撐下巴打先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都覺得有啲位係轉得太快 例如dr馮叫葉嵐小心反移情 下個鏡頭就一齊左 會唔會快左啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T04:02:19.000Z","msg":"欠缺內心掙扎戲?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9959f4213a44c768bdb716cdeb8f993f7ea1f444","tid":2101954,"uid":337444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3418cf0e8eca7be1cbc7a85a8d871ac17325f932","tid":2101954,"uid":190333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6d54ab812807eecec1f2020b07d07cb98589740","tid":2101954,"uid":337444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:32:14.000Z","msg":"睇哂全部 撐下巴打先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都覺得有啲位係轉得太快 例如dr馮叫葉嵐小心反移情 下個鏡頭就一齊左 會唔會快左啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T04:02:19.000Z","msg":"欠缺內心掙扎戲?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T05:40:27.000Z","msg":"事前其實有鋪排既 都叫有解釋<br />\n只係上一幕人地叫佢小心下一幕就一齊打左個突啫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"359e5a2a35b57bf7d003e322c2d923add3c86a51","tid":2101954,"uid":190333,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9959f4213a44c768bdb716cdeb8f993f7ea1f444","tid":2101954,"uid":337444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3418cf0e8eca7be1cbc7a85a8d871ac17325f932","tid":2101954,"uid":190333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6d54ab812807eecec1f2020b07d07cb98589740","tid":210195