\n<br />\n個人覺得套戲好好睇，好欣賞細節位，唔太覺得係多餘，美中不足係葉嵐嘅內心感受可以講多少少。個人淺見，有少少長氣，唔好介意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/28.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T12:48:36.000Z","msg":"巴打呢個見解幾特別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我都覺得葉嵐嘅內心講得太少<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e5d35399912da7d20a6fc3cea07d204dbc3575","tid":2101954,"uid":358054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"036ce413aed97873ccba8f989aad1972a7d4ee33","tid":2101954,"uid":25375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-12T18:39:41.000Z","msg":"皮已正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T12:48:58.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad04696551ac68bb9c593c01e91d8ddfe49bed5b","tid":2101954,"uid":358054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6d54ab812807eecec1f2020b07d07cb98589740","tid":2101954,"uid":337444,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T03:32:14.000Z","msg":"睇哂全部 撐下巴打先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都覺得有啲位係轉得太快 例如dr馮叫葉嵐小心反移情 下個鏡頭就一齊左 會唔會快左啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-13T12:51:05.000Z","msg":"多謝巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只可以話套戲得兩個鐘 令到好多觀眾想佢交代既野都未必有時間交代到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />所以記住睇埋小說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc960ff9c5d1f9166d3ea8b7d252e6280e730838","tid":2101954,"uid":358054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"990fb88106cd187bab971892ecaccd120e470ba8","tid":2101954,"uid":203226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ed3e9e12c0c7f74f0867c4c6da722d2adee910b5","tid":2101954